Package com.cyc.kb

KB interfaces which have not yet graduated into the official KB API portion of the Core API specification.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    LogicalConnective
    The interface for logical connectives of the CycL language, such as #$and and #$or.
    Quantifier
    The interface for Cyc quantifiers, such as #$thereExists.
    ScopingRelation
    The interface for Relations that determine the scope of one or more Variables.
    TypeFact
    The interface for Facts that are implicitly quantified over the instances of a KBCollection.
